{"tid":2308991,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[Tesla沒日] 一分鍾生產一台！恆大新車現身街頭  網民：太霸氣了","createTime":"2020-12-02T08:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T09:34:29.000Z","uid":121711,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e5fee5cad0e35515b09f41ba7eea25adaad5ed41","tid":2308991,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:53:00.000Z","msg":"作為目前中國最大嘅造車新勢力之一，恆大自宣布轉型新能源汽車領域之後就備受關注。日前，網上曝光了一組恆大新能源汽車嘅真車圖片，從車頭懸掛牌照可以睇出，該車是恆馳1，其定位為超豪華D級轎車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/7dd54f/f/800x0/https://img1.mydrivers.com/img/20201128/s_90580ba6737f44d4b2f818eeae1feae5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F7dd54f%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg1.mydrivers.com%2Fimg%2F20201128%2Fs_90580ba6737f44d4b2f818eeae1feae5.jpg&h=b42bc984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新車整體嘅設計與此前曝光嘅官圖相似，只是刪減了車頭嘅點陣式設計，採用了電動車一貫嘅封閉式設計。<br />\n<br />\n恆馳1採用了四門溜背式嘅車身設計，據悉，新車軸距達3150mm，並配備了22吋冚家鈴。此外，新車車頭上已懸掛恆大汽車正式發布嘅恆馳Logo。該Logo採用咆哮嘅雄獅作為主體設計，其寓意着「保護藍天，決勝紅海，東方雄獅，傲視全球」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/100499/f/800x0/https://img1.mydrivers.com/img/20201128/s_94de0b8cc51e4afdb90057218192b381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F100499%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg1.mydrivers.com%2Fimg%2F20201128%2Fs_94de0b8cc51e4afdb90057218192b381.png&h=2d070b69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除恆馳1車型外，恆大汽車今年8月嘅發布會上，還發佈了恆馳2、恆馳3、恆馳4、恆馳5和恆馳6，覆蓋A到D級車型，以及轎車、轎跑、靈車、SUV 和 MPV。<br />\n<br />\n目前恆大汽車上海、廣州兩大生產基地全面啟動生產，全面投產後能做到每分鍾生產1輛車。此外，恆大汽車「恆馳」系列車型預計明年下半年開始陸續量產。按照許家印未來嘅計劃，新能源車嘅產量將達到年產100萬輛，並用三到五年發展成為全世界最大、實力最強嘅新能源汽車集團。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/dc1ee1/f/800x0/https://img1.mydrivers.com/img/20201110/s_2b9616013990432fa95020c7079af630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fdc1ee1%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg1.mydrivers.com%2Fimg%2F20201110%2Fs_2b9616013990432fa95020c7079af630.jpg&h=93692810&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a773cb55e398324d611f36d5c61c8fc38bb43c7c","tid":2308991,"uid":79117,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1bc269281d6862140b0ebaefbcf2559f8878844","tid":2308991,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:54:09.000Z","msg":"一分鐘自燃"},{"pid":"6db2a6ffe1681b1ce850cc33984c8f228a79b6ed","tid":2308991,"uid":34147,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"並配備了22吋冚家鈴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04474b063ae56c4ad37d1b03d30289bd4ae56740","tid":2308991,"uid":50526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冚家鈴 靈車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382708f55791bf05c5196c40d7e4a0a9274637e3","tid":2308991,"uid":3976,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"係中國 每過60秒 就生產多一件垃圾"},{"pid":"9e2fa12cbd1e88ec09e979128afa924ae9f24f0e","tid":2308991,"uid":307999,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"搵左三架Tesla換左個副廠殼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066bafaaea7169f2571172235c806a601842f44c","tid":2308991,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:04:43.000Z","msg":"汉定含馳快d 自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eIf6K4lEOb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeIf6K4lEOb4&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2ezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=6ebdd56f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eIf6K4lEOb4</a>"},{"pid":"ec5d740bdc604